data.description: Presenting 1605 Morning Dr, a rare blend of urban and rural living along the beautiful gateway to Rocky Mountain National Park, with all of the amenities you could need right at hand! Situated on a large wooded lot, with an abundance of private outdoor space to enjoy, this 4Bd 3Ba ranch offers nearly 2,400 sq ft all on the main level in a layout that is ideal for nearly any lifestyle, with vaulted ceilings letting in tons of natural light and truly bringing the outdoors in. Among the many updates over the years including flooring, added deck space in the backyard, and more, the roof is brand new! To top it off, buyers can assume the seller's mortgage at 3.25%, with a payment of just over $2,200/month. Reach out for more details and to see this amazing home in person today!
